overview: The user initiated a comprehensive review of a sleep questionnaire
  application, providing a detailed specification and an existing Statement of
  Work. The agent performed an initial assessment, identifying several gaps and
  missing features in the current implementation. A detailed plan was then
  created, outlining high, medium, and low priority action items. The agent
  proceeded to implement the plan, successfully adding a 1-10 tiredness severity
  scale with critical safety messaging, integrating COMISA (Comorbid Insomnia
  and Sleep Apnea) detection and tailored recommendations, and implementing
  logic for Insufficient Sleep Syndrome detection and guidance. Additionally,
  placeholder outbound links to various sleep and mental health resources were
  incorporated into both the interactive web report and the downloadable PDF
  report. The implementation involved modifying types, validation schemas, UI
  components, and report generation logic across multiple files.
